overview: 2034 - Earthling Dabbill Windbag is appointed Emperor Lord Leather in the fight against intergalactic AIDS. Together with his subordinates Constable Plum and Lord Liver, he then tries to rule the galaxy. But he is opposed by the bounty hunters Schwanz Solo & Superbingowoman, who make the universe unsafe with their spaceship. A merciless and hilarious battle for space-life and space-death breaks out!
title: Warstar - Der Film
